<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Agents DeTLeng builds practical AI automation that helps teams reduce repetitive work and focus on what matters.">
  <title>AI Automation for Business | Agents DeTLeng</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Manrope:wght@600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #0b1726;
      --muted: #58687a;
      --navy: #0b1829;
      --navy-2: #10243b;
      --teal: #28d7b1;
      --teal-dark: #0b9a83;
      --lime: #c5f66d;
      --paper: #f5f8f7;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --line: #dce6e3;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(11, 23, 38, .10);
      --radius: 24px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--white);
      font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.65;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    body.menu-open { overflow: hidden; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    button { font: inherit; }
    svg { display: block; }
    .container { width: min(1160px, calc(100% - 40px)); margin-inline: auto; }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px;
      color: var(--teal-dark); font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: .14em; text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .eyebrow::before { content: ""; width: 24px; height: 2px; background: currentColor; }
    h1, h2, h3 { font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif; line-height: 1.12; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -.035em; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(3rem, 6.2vw, 5.8rem); }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(2.15rem, 4vw, 3.55rem); }
    h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; }
    p { margin: 0; }
    .section { padding: 110px 0; }
    .section-head { max-width: 760px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .section-head h2 { margin: 13px 0 18px; }
    .section-head p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.08rem; max-width: 660px; }

    .topbar {
      position: fixed; inset: 0 0 auto; z-index: 50;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.11);
      background: rgba(8, 20, 34, .78); backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }
    .nav { height: 76px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: var(--white); font-weight: 800; }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 38px; height: 38px; display: grid; place-items: center;
      border-radius: 12px; background: var(--teal); color: var(--navy);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(40,215,177,.12);
    }
    .brand-name { font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif; letter-spacing: -.02em; }
    .brand-name span { color: var(--teal); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px; color: #c9d3df; font-size: .92rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    .nav-cta { padding: 11px 18px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--teal); color: var(--navy) !important; }
    .menu-btn { display: none; border: 0; padding: 8px; color: white; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; }

    .hero {
      min-height: 820px; padding: 168px 0 100px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;
      color: var(--white); background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 78% 20%, rgba(40,215,177,.18), transparent 26%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 22% 82%, rgba(92,123,255,.13), transparent 27%),
        var(--navy);
    }
    .hero::after {
      content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: .08; pointer-events: none;
      background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.5) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.5) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 70px 70px; mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 4%, black 70%);
    }
    .hero-grid { position: relative; z-index: 1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.07fr .93fr; gap: 70px; align-items: center; }
    .hero .eyebrow { color: var(--teal); }
    .hero h1 { margin: 18px 0 26px; max-width: 750px; }
    .hero h1 em { color: var(--teal); font-style: normal; }
    .hero-copy > p { color: #bfcbd7; max-width: 650px; font-size: 1.18rem; }
    .actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14px; margin-top: 36px; }
    .btn {
      min-height: 54px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;
      padding: 0 24px; border: 1px solid transparent; border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700; transition: transform .2s, background .2s, border-color .2s;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-primary { color: var(--navy); background: var(--teal); }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #52e4c5; }
    .btn-ghost { color: var(--white); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.3); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: white; background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); }
    .trust-line { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px; margin-top: 38px; color: #a9b7c5; font-size: .88rem; }
    .trust-line span { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; }
    .trust-line i { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal); }

    .workflow-card {
      position: relative; padding: 25px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13); border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(18, 43, 67, .75); box-shadow: 0 32px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.32); backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .workflow-card::before { content: ""; position: absolute; width: 140px; height: 140px; right: -45px; top: -48px; background: var(--teal); filter: blur(80px); opacity: .28; }
    .window-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); }
    .window-dots { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .window-dots i { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: #466079; }
    .status { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; color: #9eb0c2; font-size: .75rem; }
    .status i { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(40,215,177,.12); }
    .flow { padding: 24px 0 4px; display: grid; gap: 11px; }
    .flow-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 42px 1fr auto; align-items: center; gap: 13px; padding: 14px; border-radius: 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.055); }
    .flow-icon { width: 42px; height: 42px; display: grid; place-items: center; border-radius: 12px; color: var(--teal); background: rgba(40,215,177,.12); }
    .flow-text strong { display: block; font-size: .9rem; }
    .flow-text small { color: #8fa1b4; font-size: .74rem; }
    .flow-badge { padding: 5px 8px; border-radius: 999px; color: var(--teal); background: rgba(40,215,177,.1); font-size: .66rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .metric { margin-top: 15px; padding: 18px; border-radius: 17px; color: var(--navy); background: var(--teal); }
    .metric-top { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .metric strong { font-family: "Manrope"; font-size: 1.7rem; }
    .metric small { display: block; opacity: .67; font-weight: 700; }
    .metric-bar { height: 7px; margin-top: 13px; border-radius: 9px; background: rgba(11,24,41,.14); overflow: hidden; }
    .metric-bar span { display: block; width: 78%; height: 100%; border-radius: inherit; background: var(--navy); }

    .problem { background: var(--paper); }
    .split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .9fr 1.1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }
    .split h2 { margin: 15px 0 22px; }
    .split-copy > p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .quote { margin-top: 26px; padding-left: 20px; border-left: 3px solid var(--teal-dark); color: var(--ink) !important; font-weight: 600; }
    .task-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
    .task { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; padding: 17px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 15px; background: var(--white); font-weight: 600; font-size: .92rem; box-shadow: 0 7px 24px rgba(10,36,44,.04); }
    .task i { flex: 0 0 30px; width: 30px; height: 30px; display: grid; place-items: center; border-radius: 9px; color: var(--teal-dark); background: #e3f8f3; font-style: normal; }

    .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .service-card { position: relative; overflow: hidden; min-height: 270px; padding: 29px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 20px; background: var(--white); transition: transform .25s, box-shadow .25s, border-color .25s; }
    .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: var(--shadow); border-color: transparent; }
    .service-icon { width: 52px; height: 52px; display: grid; place-items: center; margin-bottom: 27px; border-radius: 15px; color: var(--teal-dark); background: #e6faf5; }
    .service-card h3 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .service-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .95rem; }
    .service-card::after { content: attr(data-number); position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 24px; color: #cfdad7; font-family: "Manrope"; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 800; }

    .benefits { color: var(--white); background: var(--navy); }
    .benefits .section-head p { color: #aebbc8; }
    .benefits .eyebrow { color: var(--teal); }
    .benefits-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); border-radius: 22px; overflow: hidden; }
    .benefit { min-height: 190px; padding: 28px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); }
    .benefit:nth-child(4n) { border-right: 0; }
    .benefit:nth-child(n+5) { border-bottom: 0; }
    .benefit span { display: block; margin-bottom: 30px; color: var(--teal); font-family: "Manrope"; font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .benefit h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .benefit p { color: #94a5b6; font-size: .88rem; }
    .statement { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; align-items: center; margin-top: 55px; padding: 34px 38px; border-radius: 20px; color: var(--navy); background: var(--teal); }
    .statement h3 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.3vw, 2.1rem); }
    .statement p { padding-left: 34px; border-left: 1px solid rgba(11,24,41,.25); font-weight: 600; }

    .approach-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start; }
    .approach-sticky { position: sticky; top: 120px; }
    .approach-sticky h2 { margin: 15px 0 22px; }
    .approach-sticky p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .steps { counter-reset: process; }
    .step { counter-increment: process; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr; gap: 23px; padding: 29px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .step:first-child { padding-top: 0; }
    .step::before { content: "0" counter(process); width: 64px; height: 64px; display: grid; place-items: center; border-radius: 18px; color: var(--teal-dark); background: #e8f9f5; font-family: "Manrope"; font-weight: 800; }
    .step h3 { margin: 4px 0 9px; }
    .step p { color: var(--muted); }
    .size-note { margin-top: 50px; padding: 25px 28px; border-radius: 18px; background: var(--paper); }
    .size-note strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; font-family: "Manrope"; }
    .size-note p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .94rem; }

    .oversight { padding-top: 0; }
    .oversight-box { position: relative; overflow: hidden; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center; min-height: 390px; border-radius: 28px; color: var(--white); background: var(--navy-2); }
    .oversight-copy { padding: 58px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .oversight-copy .eyebrow { color: var(--teal); }
    .oversight-copy h2 { margin: 13px 0 20px; }
    .oversight-copy p { color: #adbac7; max-width: 520px; }
    .oversight-visual { height: 100%; min-height: 390px; display: grid; place-items: center; position: relative; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(40,215,177,.24), transparent 55%); }
    .human-core { position: relative; width: 130px; height: 130px; display: grid; place-items: center; border-radius: 50%; color: var(--navy); background: var(--teal); font-family: "Manrope"; font-weight: 800; box-shadow: 0 0 0 24px rgba(40,215,177,.08), 0 0 0 52px rgba(40,215,177,.04); }
    .orbit { position: absolute; width: 290px; height: 290px; border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,.25); border-radius: 50%; animation: spin 24s linear infinite; }
    .orbit i { position: absolute; width: 48px; height: 48px; display: grid; place-items: center; border-radius: 13px; color: var(--teal); background: #19344f; font-style: normal; }
    .orbit i:nth-child(1) { top: -24px; left: 121px; }
    .orbit i:nth-child(2) { bottom: 12px; left: 12px; }
    .orbit i:nth-child(3) { bottom: 12px; right: 12px; }
    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    .faq { background: var(--paper); }
    .faq-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .75fr 1.25fr; gap: 80px; align-items: start; }
    .faq-intro h2 { margin: 15px 0 18px; }
    .faq-intro p { color: var(--muted); }
    .faq-list { border-top: 1px solid #cbd8d4; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd8d4; }
    .faq-q { width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 25px; padding: 23px 0; border: 0; color: var(--ink); background: none; text-align: left; font-family: "Manrope"; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; }
    .faq-q i { flex: 0 0 30px; width: 30px; height: 30px; display: grid; place-items: center; border-radius: 50%; color: var(--teal-dark); background: var(--white); font-style: normal; transition: transform .2s; }
    .faq-a { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height .3s ease; }
    .faq-a p { padding: 0 50px 24px 0; color: var(--muted); }
    .faq-item.open .faq-q i { transform: rotate(45deg); }

    .cta { padding: 100px 0; color: var(--white); background: var(--navy); }
    .cta-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .8fr; gap: 60px; align-items: end; }
    .cta h2 { max-width: 780px; margin-top: 15px; }
    .cta .eyebrow { color: var(--teal); }
    .cta-side p { margin-bottom: 25px; color: #aebbc8; }
    .cta-side .btn { width: 100%; }

    footer { color: #9eacba; background: #071321; }
    .footer-main { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .8fr .8fr; gap: 50px; padding: 58px 0 44px; }
    .footer-brand p { max-width: 390px; margin-top: 18px; font-size: .91rem; }
    .footer-col strong { display: block; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--white); font-family: "Manrope"; }
    .footer-col a { display: block; width: fit-content; margin: 9px 0; font-size: .9rem; }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--teal); }
    .footer-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 30px; padding: 22px 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); font-size: .8rem; }

    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity .65s ease, transform .65s ease; }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 76px 0 auto; flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; padding: 30px 20px; color: var(--white); background: var(--navy); }
      .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
      .nav-links a { padding: 7px 0; }
      .nav-cta { text-align: center; }
      .menu-btn { display: block; }
      .hero { padding-top: 140px; }
      .hero-grid, .split, .approach-grid, .faq-grid, .cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-grid { gap: 60px; }
      .workflow-card { max-width: 620px; }
      .split { gap: 45px; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .benefit:nth-child(2n) { border-right: 0; }
      .benefit:nth-child(n+5) { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); }
      .benefit:nth-child(n+7) { border-bottom: 0; }
      .statement { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; }
      .statement p { padding: 20px 0 0; border-left: 0; border-top: 1px solid rgba(11,24,41,.25); }
      .approach-sticky { position: static; }
      .oversight-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .faq-grid { gap: 38px; }
      .cta-inner { align-items: start; }
      .cta-side { max-width: 560px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 650px) {
      .container { width: min(100% - 28px, 1160px); }
      .section { padding: 78px 0; }
      h1 { font-size: clamp(2.55rem, 13vw, 4rem); }
      h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .hero { min-height: auto; padding: 124px 0 74px; }
      .hero-grid { gap: 46px; }
      .hero-copy > p { font-size: 1.05rem; }
      .actions .btn { width: 100%; }
      .trust-line { gap: 12px 20px; }
      .workflow-card { padding: 17px; border-radius: 21px; }
      .flow-row { grid-template-columns: 39px 1fr; }
      .flow-badge { display: none; }
      .task-list, .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .service-card { min-height: 235px; }
      .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .benefit, .benefit:nth-child(2n), .benefit:nth-child(n+7) { border-right: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); }
      .benefit:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
      .statement { padding: 28px; }
      .step { grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr; gap: 17px; }
      .step::before { width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 15px; }
      .oversight-copy { padding: 36px 26px; }
      .oversight-visual { min-height: 330px; }
      .orbit { width: 250px; height: 250px; }
      .orbit i:nth-child(1) { left: 101px; }
      .footer-main { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 7px; }
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
      *, *::before, *::after { animation-duration: .01ms !important; animation-iteration-count: 1 !important; transition-duration: .01ms !important; }
      .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="Agents DeTLeng home">
        <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M7 17 17 7M8 7h9v9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        <span class="brand-name">Agents <span>DeTLeng</span></span>
      </a>
      <nav class="nav-links" id="navLinks" aria-label="Main navigation">
        <a href="#automation">Automation</a><a href="#solutions">Solutions</a><a href="#approach">Our approach</a><a href="#faq">FAQ</a><a class="nav-cta" href="#contact">Start a conversation</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="menu-btn" id="menuBtn" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navLinks" aria-label="Open menu">
        <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M4 7h16M4 12h16M4 17h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">Practical AI automation</span>
          <h1>Give your team an AI that handles <em>repetitive work.</em></h1>
          <p>Reduce repetitive tasks. Save valuable time. Let your people focus on work that truly matters.</p>
          <div class="actions"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Explore automation <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a><a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#solutions">See what AI can do</a></div>
          <div class="trust-line"><span><i></i>Built around your workflows</span><span><i></i>Human oversight</span><span><i></i>Practical outcomes</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="workflow-card reveal" aria-label="AI workflow overview">
          <div class="window-head"><div class="window-dots"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div><span class="status"><i></i>AI assistant active</span></div>
          <div class="flow">
            <div class="flow-row"><span class="flow-icon">✉</span><span class="flow-text"><strong>Customer enquiry</strong><small>Reply drafted and routed</small></span><span class="flow-badge">DONE</span></div>
            <div class="flow-row"><span class="flow-icon">⌕</span><span class="flow-text"><strong>Document request</strong><small>Policy found in 1.2 seconds</small></span><span class="flow-badge">FOUND</span></div>
            <div class="flow-row"><span class="flow-icon">↗</span><span class="flow-text"><strong>Weekly report</strong><small>Summary prepared for review</small></span><span class="flow-badge">READY</span></div>
            <div class="flow-row"><span class="flow-icon">✓</span><span class="flow-text"><strong>Sales follow-up</strong><small>Personalized email scheduled</small></span><span class="flow-badge">QUEUED</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric"><div class="metric-top"><span><strong>78%</strong><small>Routine work handled</small></span><svg width="31" height="31" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="m5 15 4-4 3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div><div class="metric-bar"><span></span></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section problem" id="automation">
      <div class="container split">
